                                        <input class="form-control" type="text" title="" value="" name="form[storage_ip]">
                                    </div>
                                    <span class="help-inline col-xs-12 col-sm-12">
                                        <span class="small txt-default">IP-адрес хранилища. Пример: http://127.0.0.1</span>
